      "content": "hey, looking at the specs for the Apex industrial drills. we're considering a fleet order for our night shift operations, but the runtime is the make or break for us. can you confirm the battery actually handles a full 24-hour cycle of heavy use without needing a swap? we can't have downtime mid-shift.",
