    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a rotation schedule means more downtime and more equipment to manage, which honestly doesn't work for our workflow. we need a tool that just stays running. if the drill can't hit that 24-hour mark on a single charge under load, we'll have to pass on this order and look at other manufacturers who can meet that spec. are you sure there's no way to hit 24 hours?",
